IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_STPRPClockingHeadCountDaily') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STPRPClockingHeadCountDaily
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STPRPClockingHeadCountDaily (
    [prp_clockingheadcountdaily_date] date,
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_division] nvarchar(4000),
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_costcentredescription] nvarchar(4000),
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_costcentrecode] nvarchar(4000),
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_teamname] nvarchar(4000),
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_payroll] nvarchar(4000),
    [prp_clockingheadcountdaily_jobcategory] nvarchar(4000),
	[prp_clockingheadcountdaily_clockingcount] int



	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/FINANCE/stprpclockingheadcountdaily.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.T_STPRPClockingHeadCountDaily --where prp_clockinghoursdaily_date is not NULL
GO
